<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> kulottuṅkacoḻatevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="18"><g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num><g type="dash"/>vatu Uṭaiyār tiruvaṇṇāmalaiyuṭaiya nāyanāṟku malaiyaṉ viṉaiyveṉṟāṉāṉa <unclear>ka</unclear>rikālacoḻa Ā<unclear>ṭai</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yūrṉāṭāḻvāneṉ ciṟukālaicantikku tirumantirapuvaṉappuṟamāka<note n="62-1">Read poṉakappuṟamāka.</note>viṭṭa perumākkaṭappāṉa viṉaiyveṉṟanallūr nāṟpāl Ellaiyum <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>kku Ūru<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> cantirātittavarai celvatāka kal veṭṭikkuṭutteṉ karikālacoḻa <unclear>Āṭaiyūrnāṭāḻvāneṉ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Itu viṭuvittāṉ Amarapuyaṅkaraperumāḷ <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied> Itu paṉ<hi rend="grantha">mā heśvara rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

